{{Infobox language |name=Sokoro |states=[[Chad]] |region=central |speakers=5,000 |date=1994 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Afro-Asiatic |fam2=[[Chadic languages|Chadic]] |fam3=[[East Chadic languages|East Chadic]] |fam4=[[East Chadic B languages|East Chadic B]] |fam5=[[Sokoro languages|Sokoro]] (B.3) |iso3=sok |glotto=soko1263 |glottorefname=Sokoro }}
'''Sokoro''' is an [[Afro-Asiatic languages|Afro-Asiatic]] language spoken in central [[Chad]]. Dialects are Bedanga and Sokoro.<ref name=e18/>
